		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="#regest1">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto ad te, quas heri accepi, Welseri nostri literas<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Hans Welsers Brief, 4. März (<ref target="files.xml#12416">Nr. 2369</ref>).</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad me, puto, eadem de pontificis<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Paul III.</note> conatibus scripsit<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Nicht in <hi><persName ref="19">Blarer</persName> BW.</hi></note>; quod caesari<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Karl V.</note> promiserit 700M libra se impensurum in concilii<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Das Konzil zu <placeName ref="1089">Trient</placeName>.</note> exquutionem<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">= executionem.</note>, si ad hanc gladio accingi velit<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Siehe schon <ref target="files.xml#12375">Nr. 2328</ref>, Anm. 44. - Vgl. Welsers Brief an Bullinger, wo er, allerdings ohne Angabe einer Geldsumme, diese Nachricht auch übermittelt (<ref target="files.xml#12416">Nr. 2369</ref>,22-27).</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus filium istum perditionis<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">Der Papst. - Vgl. 2Thess 2, 3.</note>, qui bonos omnes perditos tantopere cupit, quamprimum perdat in gloriam regni Christi sui!</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div2" corresp="#regest2">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale et ora pro nobis.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta amicos et fratres.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">9. martii.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus A. Bl.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. Heinricho Bullingero, suo fratri colendissimo.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
